sections.TOP: Game of Thrones Season 4 Soundtrack026150o9cfnwwla8k08rnt7b69ygeuuk4punu1455482014-06-17T07:42:32ZValyrian Plastic24814998Adding categoriesThe '''Game of Thrones Season 4 Soundtrack''' was composed by [http://gameofthrones.wikia.com/wiki/Ramin_Djawadi Ramin Djawadi] and was released on June 10, 2014. It was preceded by the ''[http://gameofthrones.wikia.com/wiki/Game_of_Thrones_Season_3_Soundtrack Game of Thrones Season 3 Soundtrack]'', released in 2013.
